summary: ...TROPICAL STORM WATCHES ISSUED FOR PORTIONS OF THE NORTHERN LEEWARD ISLANDS... As of 5:00 PM AST Tue Oct 07 the center of Jerry was located near 12.0, -46.4 with movement W at 23 mph. The minimum central pressure was 1003 mb with maximum sustained winds of about 50 mph.
